Randy Quaid

Alive

Born: 10/1/1950 in Houston, Texas, USA

Age: 73

Full name: Randall Rudy Quaid

Noted For: actor, Vacation (1983), "Saturday Night Live" (1985-86), Brokeback Mountain (2005). Older brother of actor Dennis Quaid.
